snippet.title: "Kokomi: A Thousand Waves Under the Moon" Piano Cover | Genshin Impact Character Demo OST
snippet.description:
Genshin Impact - Kokomi Demo 「A Thousand Waves Under the Moon」 OST Piano Performance


I played the 'Kokomi' demo "A Thousand Waves Under the Moon" on the piano.
She is The 5-star character, which is rerunning with the pickup in the second half of version 3.8

She almost became a character of misfortune due to timing and performance in the past
From the time it started to be re-examined until now, in high-difficulty content, She is firmly established.

So sweet and mysterious music!!
This is one of the PVs with really fantastic visuals.

Thank you for listening.

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
Nilou's 'Dance of Sabzeruz' Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/Ab97Db-3FiU
Aranara's Theme Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/YJtCY1zp94Y
'Dori' theme Insane Piano Duet Performance : https://youtu.be/7gAj7fL8edg
Collei Demo 「Sprout in the Thicket」 Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/4_P8vIO2EXI
-----------------------------------------------
템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
Illust : https://www.pixiv.net/artworks/93044999
